@startuml
actor "Admin" as A
participant "Frontend" as F
participant "Banner API" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB

A -> F: Xem danh sách Banner
F -> API: GET /api/admin/banners
API -> DB: find()
DB --> API: bannerList
API --> F: 200 OK
F --> A: Render Component

A -> F: Lưu Banner (Kèm Upload Ảnh)
F -> API: POST (Multipart) /api/admin/banners
API -> API: Upload & Save Image URL
API -> DB: insert() 
DB --> API: doc
API --> F: 201 Created
F --> A: "Thêm Banner Thành Công"
@enduml
